[% META
        title = "AI Chat System Complete Audit"
   description = "Comprehensive audit of Comserv AI chat systems including schema analysis, data flow, missing data issues, and recommendations. Updated Jan 2 with metadata column fix."
   roles = "admin,developer"
   TemplateType = "Documentation"
   category = "database,audit,ai"
   page_version = "1.01"
   last_updated = "Thu Jan 02 15:42:00 UTC 2026"
   site_specific = "false"
%]
[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/ai_chat_system_audit.tt,v 1.01 2026/01/02 15:42:00 zencoder Exp zencoder - Jan 2 Update: Metadata column fix applied to ai_conversations table' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">AI Chat System - Complete Audit Report</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        Audit Date: 2025-12-27 | 
        Version: 1.01 (Updated Jan 2) | 
        Audit Type: Complete System Analysis (Schema + Code + Data Flow) | 
        Status: Complete
    </div>

    <!-- RECENT CHANGES -->
    <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">Recent Changes (Jan 2, 2026)</h3>
        <ul style="margin: 10px 0; color: #856404;">
            <li><strong>Schema Fix Applied</strong>: Missing metadata column added to ai_conversations table. Production database at 192.168.1.198:3306 updated with: ALTER TABLE ai_conversations ADD COLUMN metadata longtext NULL AFTER status;</li>
            <li><strong>Impact</strong>: AI Chat System message creation regression fixed. Future conversation/message persistence now operational.</li>
            <li><strong>Data Loss Note</strong>: 17 conversations created Dec 27-30 during regression still have 0 messages. Recommend testing with fresh conversation post-fix.</li>
            <li><strong>Related Work</strong>: See Chat 1 in DAILY_AUDIT_2026-01-02.md for complete details of this fix.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Executive Summary</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                Comserv contains <strong>two separate chat systems</strong> with distinct architectures, tables, and purposes. 
                The modern AI Chat system is fully functional, while the legacy Basic Chat system lacks proper ORM integration. 
                Multiple advanced features are defined in the database schema but not yet implemented in application code.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-50">
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--success-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--success-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">System 1: AI Chat (Modern)</h3>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>Tables</strong>: ai_conversations, ai_messages</li>
                    <li><strong>Status</strong>: ✅ IMPLEMENTED & ACTIVELY USED</li>
                    <li><strong>Controller</strong>: Comserv::Controller::AI</li>
                    <li><strong>ORM Model</strong>: ✅ Complete with relationships</li>
                    <li><strong>Data Persistence</strong>: ✅ Working correctly</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-50">
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">System 2: Basic Chat (Legacy)</h3>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <li><strong>Table</strong>: chat_messages</li>
                    <li><strong>Status</strong>: ⚠️ IMPLEMENTED but NO ORM MODEL</li>
                    <li><strong>Controller</strong>: Comserv::Controller::Chat</li>
                    <li><strong>ORM Model</strong>: ❌ MISSING</li>
                    <li><strong>Data Access</strong>: Raw database queries</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SYSTEM 1: AI CHAT -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">System 1: AI Chat (Modern Implementation)</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                The modern AI Chat system provides conversation history, message metadata, and search indexing capabilities. 
                Built with proper DBIx::Class ORM models and full Perl Catalyst integration.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI CONVERSATIONS TABLE -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Table: ai_conversations</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <strong>Purpose</strong>: Container for grouped AI chat messages within a conversation<br/>
                <strong>Model File</strong>: lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/AiConversation.pm<br/>
                <strong>Status</strong>: ✅ Properly modeled with DBIx::Class
            </p>
            
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0; font-size: 0.85em;"><code>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ai_conversations (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    title VARCHAR(255) NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    status ENUM('active', 'archived') DEFAULT 'active',
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id)
);</code></pre>
            </div>

            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <tr>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Column</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Type</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Nullable</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Notes</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>id</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">INT</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">No</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Primary key, auto-increment</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>user_id</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">INT</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">No</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FK to users table</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>title</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">VARCHAR(255)</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Yes</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Conversation title</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>created_at</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">TIMESTAMP</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">No</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Conversation start time</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>updated_at</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">TIMESTAMP</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">No</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Last message time</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>status</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">ENUM</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">No</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">'active' or 'archived'</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI MESSAGES TABLE -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Table: ai_messages</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <strong>Purpose</strong>: Individual user and AI messages within a conversation<br/>
                <strong>Model File</strong>: lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/AiMessage.pm<br/>
                <strong>Status</strong>: ✅ Properly modeled with DBIx::Class and relationships
            </p>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0; font-size: 0.8em;"><code>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ai_messages (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    conversation_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NULL,
    role ENUM('user', 'assistant') NOT NULL,
    content LONGTEXT NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    metadata JSON NULL,
    agent_type ENUM('documentation', 'helpdesk', 'ency', 'beekeeping', 'hamradio'),
    model_used VARCHAR(100) NULL,
    search_context JSON NULL,
    sources_cited JSON NULL,
    user_role VARCHAR(100) NULL,
    response_time_ms INT NULL,
    tokens_used INT NULL,
    is_verified BOOLEAN DEFAULT 0,
    ip_address VARCHAR(45) NULL
);</code></pre>
            </div>

            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <tr>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Column</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Type</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Purpose</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>id</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">INT</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Message ID, primary key</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>conversation_id</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">INT</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">FK to ai_conversations</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>role</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">ENUM</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">'user' or 'assistant'</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>content</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">LONGTEXT</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Message text</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>model_used</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">VARCHAR(100)</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Name of model that generated response</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>sources_cited</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">JSON</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">⚠️ Never populated - citation tracking not implemented</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>search_context</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">JSON</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">⚠️ Always NULL - documentation search not integrated</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>ip_address</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">VARCHAR(45)</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">User IP for audit trail</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI DATA FLOW -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">AI Chat Data Flow</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                Complete flow from user message through AI processing to database persistence:
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Step 1: User Initiates Chat</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Route</strong>: POST /ai/chat<br/>
                    <strong>Controller</strong>: Comserv::Controller::AI::chat() (Line 492)<br/>
                    <strong>Input</strong>: prompt (required), conversation_id (optional), model (optional)
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Step 2: Create or Fetch Conversation</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Code</strong>: AI.pm Lines 670-688<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Creates new ai_conversations record if no ID provided<br/>
                    <strong>Data Stored</strong>: user_id, title, status='active', timestamps
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Step 3: Save User Message</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Code</strong>: AI.pm Lines 694-704<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Creates ai_messages record with role='user'<br/>
                    <strong>Data</strong>: prompt content, user_id, agent_type, model_used, ip_address, user_role
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Step 4: Query Ollama LLM</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Service</strong>: External Ollama server (localhost or network)<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Send prompt, receive generated response<br/>
                    <strong>No Persistence</strong>: Response not stored until Step 5
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Step 5: Save AI Response</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Code</strong>: AI.pm Lines 713-726<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Creates ai_messages record with role='assistant'<br/>
                    <strong>Data</strong>: full response, performance metrics (duration, eval_count), metadata
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Step 6: Return to User</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Format</strong>: JSON response<br/>
                    <strong>Data</strong>: response content, model used, conversation_id, performance metrics
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MISSING DATA ISSUES -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Critical Missing Data Issues</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                The following data is defined in the database schema but never populated or used by application code:
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Issue 1: web_search_results Table Completely Unused</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Severity</strong>: HIGH<br/>
                    <strong>Status</strong>: Zero entries ever created<br/>
                    <strong>Expected Use</strong>: Store verified web search results for AI citations<br/>
                    <strong>Current Reality</strong>: No code creates entries, no code reads entries<br/>
                    <strong>Impact</strong>: Web search feature non-functional; table serves no purpose<br/>
                    <strong>Recommendation</strong>: Either implement web search or remove table
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Issue 2: sources_cited Column Always NULL</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Severity</strong>: HIGH<br/>
                    <strong>Column</strong>: ai_messages.sources_cited (JSON)<br/>
                    <strong>Expected Use</strong>: Track which sources/documents AI cited in response<br/>
                    <strong>Current Reality</strong>: Never written to in AI.pm controller<br/>
                    <strong>Impact</strong>: Users cannot see sources for AI responses; audit trail incomplete<br/>
                    <strong>Recommendation</strong>: Implement citation tracking in Ollama integration
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Issue 3: search_context Always NULL</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Severity</strong>: MEDIUM<br/>
                    <strong>Column</strong>: ai_messages.search_context (JSON)<br/>
                    <strong>Expected Use</strong>: Capture which documentation was searched before generating response<br/>
                    <strong>Current Reality</strong>: documentation_metadata_index table built but never queried<br/>
                    <strong>Impact</strong>: Search history lost; cannot verify documentation relevance<br/>
                    <strong>Recommendation</strong>: Query documentation index before Ollama call, store results
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Issue 4: Documentation Metadata Index Not Populated</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Severity</strong>: HIGH<br/>
                    <strong>Table</strong>: documentation_metadata_index<br/>
                    <strong>Expected Use</strong>: Full-text searchable index of .tt files<br/>
                    <strong>Current Reality</strong>: Table exists, no code populates it<br/>
                    <strong>Impact</strong>: AI cannot search documentation; search_context feature impossible<br/>
                    <strong>Recommendation</strong>: Implement documentation indexing script and job scheduler
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Issue 5: Code Search Index Not Used</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Severity</strong>: MEDIUM<br/>
                    <strong>Table</strong>: code_search_index<br/>
                    <strong>Expected Use</strong>: Enable developer/admin queries on codebase<br/>
                    <strong>Current Reality</strong>: Table exists, no code populates or queries it<br/>
                    <strong>Impact</strong>: Code search feature for developers non-functional<br/>
                    <strong>Recommendation</strong>: Implement code indexing and search API
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SYSTEM 2: BASIC CHAT -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">System 2: Basic Chat (Legacy Implementation)</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                Simple user-to-admin messaging system. Functional but uses raw database access without ORM model.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Table: chat_messages</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <strong>Purpose</strong>: Simple user-to-admin messaging<br/>
                <strong>Model File</strong>: ❌ MISSING<br/>
                <strong>Status</strong>: ⚠️ Data persisting but using raw database access<br/>
                <strong>Controller</strong>: Comserv::Controller::Chat
            </p>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0; font-size: 0.85em;"><code>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS chat_messages (
    id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    username VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    message TEXT NOT NULL,
    timestamp VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    is_read BOOLEAN DEFAULT 0,
    is_system_message BOOLEAN DEFAULT 0,
    recipient_username VARCHAR(255),
    domain VARCHAR(255),
    site_name VARCHAR(255)
);</code></pre>
            </div>

            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <tr>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Column</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Type</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Purpose</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>id</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">INTEGER</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Primary key</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>username</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">VARCHAR(255)</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Sender username (or 'Guest')</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>timestamp</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">VARCHAR(255)</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">⚠️ Stored as string, not TIMESTAMP type</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>is_system_message</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">BOOLEAN</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">System vs user message flag</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><code>recipient_username</code></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">VARCHAR(255)</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Intended recipient for responses</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Critical Issue: Missing ChatMessage ORM Model</h3>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Problem</strong>: Controller uses raw database access instead of proper DBIx::Class model<br/>
                    <strong>File</strong>: lib/Comserv/Controller/Chat.pm<br/>
                    <strong>Code</strong>: Uses <code>$c->model('DB::ChatMessage')</code> without ChatMessage.pm model file<br/>
                    <strong>Impact</strong>: Technical debt; no relationships, no validation, no ORM integration<br/>
                    <strong>Solution</strong>: Create lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/ChatMessage.pm
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

