                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">1. Create ChatMessage DBIx::Class Model</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>File</strong>: lib/Comserv/Model/Schema/Ency/Result/ChatMessage.pm<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Create proper ORM model for chat_messages table<br/>
                    <strong>Update</strong>: Modify Chat.pm controller to use model instead of raw DB access<br/>
                    <strong>Effort</strong>: 2-3 hours<br/>
                    <strong>Benefit</strong>: Proper ORM integration, type safety, relationship support
                </p>
