                    <strong>Feature</strong>: Web search integration with AI responses<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Implement web search in AI.pm controller<br/>
                    <strong>Persist</strong>: Write WebSearchResult records, link via used_in_ai_message_id<br/>
                    <strong>Effort</strong>: 4-5 hours<br/>
                    <strong>Benefit</strong>: Citation tracking, audit trail of sources used
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">3. Implement Source Citation Tracking</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Feature</strong>: Track and display which sources AI cited<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Populate ai_messages.sources_cited JSON column<br/>
                    <strong>Display</strong>: Show citations in AI responses and UI<br/>
                    <strong>Effort</strong>: 3-4 hours<br/>
                    <strong>Benefit</strong>: Transparency, verifiability, compliance
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

