                    <strong>Effort</strong>: 4-5 hours<br/>
                    <strong>Benefit</strong>: More accurate AI responses, documented source knowledge
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">5. Auto-generate Conversation Titles</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Feature</strong>: Auto-generated titles for conversations<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Extract first message content, generate title from first 50 chars<br/>
                    <strong>Update</strong>: Refresh title on significant messages<br/>
                    <strong>Effort</strong>: 1-2 hours<br/>
                    <strong>Benefit</strong>: Better conversation organization, improved UX
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <h4 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">6. Implement AI Model Configuration</h4>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                    <strong>Feature</strong>: Dynamic model configuration per user role<br/>
                    <strong>Action</strong>: Move hardcoded model selection to ai_model_config table<br/>
                    <strong>Benefit</strong>: Role-based model restrictions, dynamic configuration<br/>
                    <strong>Effort</strong>: 3-4 hours
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

